      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The longitudinal chassis remains structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, paired with a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical variable M differential lock. Suspension geometry is tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with linear power delivery. This is a mechanically robust example ready for the B-roads.",
