    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a standout example of BMW\u2019s high-revving, naturally aspirated peak, featuring the S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. The powertrain utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to provide exceptional throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Critically, this chassis has undergone rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the communicative steering feel and balanced weight distribution this platform is known for. While the exterior shows minor signs of use typical of a driven enthusiast car, the mechanical components are synchronized and robust, making it a prime candidate for a spirited daily or weekend canyon car.",
